  <entry>
    <title>介质访问控制-静态划分信道</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2022/03/18/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/%E4%BB%8B%E8%B4%A8%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2022/03/18/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/%E4%BB%8B%E8%B4%A8%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81/</id>
    <published>2022-03-18T12:20:11.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-03-18T12:23:17.412Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="传输数据使用的两种链路"><a href="#传输数据使用的两种链路" class="headerlink" title="传输数据使用的两种链路"></a>传输数据使用的两种链路</h1><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203181324256.png" alt="image-20220318132400110"></p><h1 id="介质访问控制"><a href="#介质访问控制" class="headerlink" title="介质访问控制"></a>介质访问控制</h1><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203181325238.png" alt="image-20220318132511094"></p><h2 id="静态划分信道-信道划分介质访问控制"><a href="#静态划分信道-信道划分介质访问控制" class="headerlink" title="静态划分信道-信道划分介质访问控制"></a>静态划分信道-信道划分介质访问控制</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203181327042.png" alt="image-20220318132720901"></p><h3 id="频分多路复用FDM"><a href="#频分多路复用FDM" class="headerlink" title="频分多路复用FDM"></a>频分多路复用FDM</h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203181329955.png" alt="image-20220318132922818"></p><h3 id="时分多路复用TDM"><a href="#时分多路复用TDM" class="headerlink" title="时分多路复用TDM"></a>时分多路复用TDM</h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203181332029.png" alt="image-20220318133206900"></p><ul><li>并行：同时向前推进。</li><li>并发：一人占用一个时间片。</li></ul><h3 id="改进的时分复用-统计时分复用STDM"><a href="#改进的时分复用-统计时分复用STDM" class="headerlink" title="改进的时分复用-统计时分复用STDM"></a>改进的时分复用-统计时分复用STDM</h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203181335584.png" alt="image-20220318133519438"></p><h3 id="波分多路复用WDM"><a href="#波分多路复用WDM" class="headerlink" title="波分多路复用WDM"></a>波分多路复用WDM</h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203181336439.png" alt="image-20220318133616305"></p><h3 id="码分多路复用CDM"><a href="#码分多路复用CDM" class="headerlink" title="码分多路复用CDM"></a>码分多路复用CDM</h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203181341568.png" alt="image-20220318134109419"></p><ul><li>规格化内积：对应位相乘再相加最后除以总位数。</li><li>相互正交：规格化内积等于0。</li><li>线性相加：各个位相加即可。</li></ul><h2 id="CD和CS的混淆"><a href="#CD和CS的混淆" class="headerlink" title="CD和CS的混淆"></a>CD和CS的混淆</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203181348253.png" alt="image-20220318134835114"></p>]]></content>
    
    
