    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="后退N帧协议（GBN）"><a href="#后退N帧协议（GBN）" class="headerlink" title="后退N帧协议（GBN）"></a>后退N帧协议（GBN）</h1><h2 id="停等协议的弊端"><a href="#停等协议的弊端" class="headerlink" title="停等协议的弊端"></a>停等协议的弊端</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203181229817.png" alt="image-20220318122928649"></p><h2 id="后退N帧协议的滑动窗口"><a href="#后退N帧协议的滑动窗口" class="headerlink" title="后退N帧协议的滑动窗口"></a>后退N帧协议的滑动窗口</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203181233552.png" alt="image-20220318123335410"></p><h2 id="发送方"><a href="#发送方" class="headerlink" title="发送方"></a>发送方</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203181236696.png" alt="image-20220318123640539"></p><h2 id="接收方"><a href="#接收方" class="headerlink" title="接收方"></a>接收方</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203181238157.png" alt="image-20220318123855013"></p><h2 id="运行流程"><a href="#运行流程" class="headerlink" title="运行流程"></a>运行流程</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203181248042.png" alt="image-20220318124854887"></p><h2 id="滑动窗口长度的问题"><a href="#滑动窗口长度的问题" class="headerlink" title="滑动窗口长度的问题"></a>滑动窗口长度的问题</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203181250910.png" alt="image-20220318125040786"></p><h2 id="GBN协议重点总结"><a href="#GBN协议重点总结" class="headerlink" title="GBN协议重点总结"></a>GBN协议重点总结</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203181252651.png" alt="image-20220318125225507"></p><h2 id="练习题"><a href="#练习题" class="headerlink" title="练习题"></a>练习题</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203181253569.png" alt="image-20220318125342436"></p><ul><li>接收方一定是按序接收并发送的确认帧。</li></ul><h1 id="GBN协议的性能分析"><a href="#GBN协议的性能分析" class="headerlink" title="GBN协议的性能分析"></a>GBN协议的性能分析</h1><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203181256026.png" alt="image-20220318125617865"></p><h1 id="脑图时刻"><a href="#脑图时刻" class="headerlink" title="脑图时刻"></a>脑图时刻</h1><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203181256398.png" alt="image-20220318125633275"></p>]]></content>
    
    
