    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="辅音字母得发音规则"><a href="#辅音字母得发音规则" class="headerlink" title="辅音字母得发音规则"></a>辅音字母得发音规则</h1><h2 id="不发音的辅音字母"><a href="#不发音的辅音字母" class="headerlink" title="不发音的辅音字母"></a>不发音的辅音字母</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203131239259.png" alt="image-20220313123934143"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203131241992.png" alt="image-20220313124104887"></p><ul><li>发音</li></ul><hr><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203131242473.png" alt="image-20220313124220355"></p><hr><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203131243818.png" alt="image-20220313124359685"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203131247936.png" alt="image-20220313124727824"></p><ul><li>由于h在exh中不发音，所以忽略h，所以ex是在元音a的前面，发音不同。</li></ul><hr><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203131250580.png" alt="image-20220313125011454"></p><hr><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203131251629.png" alt="image-20220313125151510"></p><h2 id="发音的辅音字母"><a href="#发音的辅音字母" class="headerlink" title="发音的辅音字母"></a>发音的辅音字母</h2><ul><li>有规则，考一个对一个</li></ul><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203131254288.png" alt="image-20220313125447139"></p><ul><li>第三个发音：Sure、sugar、Russia  只有三个单词    </li></ul><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203131300871.png" alt="image-20220313130053749"></p><ul><li>raise a dog  养狗</li><li>单词中有前缀是把他去掉，例如：consist，去掉con，s位于词首，属于（1）的情况。</li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
